Package sorcer.util.bdb.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MarshalledData
    A MarshalledData serves as the data in the key/data pair for multiple entities.
    ObjectInfo
    RecordInfo defines the object record format for SORCER data storage services.
    SorcerDatabase
    SorcerDatabase defines the storage containers, indices and foreign keys for the service provider database persisting common SORCER objects.
    SorcerDatabaseViews
    ExertionDatabaseViews defines the data bindings and collection views for the exertion database.
    SorcerDatabaseViews.ContextBinding
    ContextBinding is used to bind the stored key/data entry pair to a combined data object (entity).
    SorcerDatabaseViews.UuidObjectBinding
    ObjectBinding is used to bind the stored key/data entry pair to a combined data object (entity).
    UuidKey
    A Uuid key serves as the key in the key/data pair for multiple entities.
    UuidObject
    A UuidObject serves as the Uuid/Object pair for persisted entities.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Store
    Extracted from SorcerDatabaseViews
